  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: bea5fab33c81bfa4c880b76261b3e542, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Comment: 'Every System should have both a singleton refering to its own class,
    as well as a BaseSystem MonoBehaviour to put data into.


    Then, Reign should
    contain a list of all systems and a way to ''get'' them using the name typed
    into the BaseSystem.'
